CBRE is pleased to present 27-33 Raglan Street, South Melbourne for lease. Situated in trendy South Melbourne, this office provides light filled office accommodation across two levels with excellent access to all the amenity South Melbourne has on offer, including MSAC, Albert Park Lake, Rising Sun Hotel and Albert Eastern Café only metres away.

Office features:
-	Reception area
-	Large boardroom
-	Offices and meeting rooms
-	Open plan workstations
-	Male and Female facilities 
-	Kitchen
-	Secure car parking

For more information or to arrange an inspection please contact Jamie Allen or Josh Jennings.

CBRE is pleased to present the best creative building in South Melbourne. 163 Eastern Road has recently undergone a major refurbishment to include new on floor bathrooms, showers and kitchens, positioning the building as one of South Melbourne’s most desirable creative buildings. The building has an entertainment roof top space with access for all tenants and equipped with seating, bar and converted caravan for events. 

The tenancies will feature exposed services and concrete flooring/timber floors throughout, offering a creative style work environment while capturing fantastic views out across Albert Park Lake. The building also benefits from its proximity to retail including Mr Albert Eastern café and lifestyle amenity at MSAC/Albert Park Lake.

Level 1 : 170 sqm – Fully fitted - LEASED
Level 2 : 134 sqm – Fully fitted
Level 4 : 85sqm - Fully fitted
Level 5 : 471 sqm – Fully refurbished 
Level 7 : PENTHOUSE OFFICE 330 sqm with internal courtyard – Fully fitted - LEASED

Key features include:

- Creatively refurbished whole floor
- Shower facilities
- Car parking available
- Access to spectacular rooftop terrace fitted with bar and entertainment facilities with views over the lake 


Please contact Joshua Jennings for more information or to arrange an inspection.

Tiga Commercial and CBRE are proud to present for lease 102 Albert Road, South Melbourne. 

Occupying a prominent city fringe location just to the west of the Kingsway and Albert Road intersection, the property comprises of a modern 5 level office building, with secure basement car parking on-site. The building benefits from excellent natural light with the upper levels having views of both Albert Park and Southbank.

Tenants at 102 Albert Road, South Melbourne enjoy excellent surrounding amenities with several popular cafes and eateries adjacent to the building and scenic parklands including Albert Park and The Royal Botanic Gardens close by. 
 
Current availabilities:

 Ground floor retail: 111.2sqm
Level 1: 435sqm
Level 4: 390sqm
Level 5: 1,070sqm (Ability to be split from 300sqm)

For further information, or to arrange an inspection please contact the listed agents.

Retail operators and businesses take your pick! Rare opportunity exists in the highly sought after fringe suburban of South Melbourne.

Ground Floor opportunity available to a wide range of uses (STCA) which has prime corner exposure.
